Because of the opposite angle theorem,

15
00:00:50,496 --> 00:00:54,416
notice also that this angle is 90 degrees, as is this angle.

16
00:00:54,416 --> 00:00:57,328
Meaning that the two triangles share two angles.

17
00:00:58,328 --> 00:01:00,465
They must also share the third angle,

18
00:01:00,465 --> 00:01:04,193
because all three angles must add up to 180 degrees.

19
00:01:05,193 --> 00:01:09,064
